Uses of Package
ch.ethz.vizzly.datatype

  • Packages that use ch.ethz.vizzly.datatype 
    Package Description
    ch.ethz.vizzly
    This package includes the Java servlet, the output generation and the Vizzly state container.
    ch.ethz.vizzly.cache
    This package contains interface definitions and common functionalities for implementing a cache.
    ch.ethz.vizzly.cache.memory
    This package contains the implementation of a memory cache.
    ch.ethz.vizzly.cache.sqldb
    This package contains the implementation of a cache that stores aggregated data in a SQL database.
    ch.ethz.vizzly.datareader
    This package contains common classes for data reader and the implementation of a CSV file reader.
    ch.ethz.vizzly.datareader.gsn
    This package contains the implementation of a data reader that fetched data over HTTP from a GSN server.
    ch.ethz.vizzly.datatype
    This package contains the implementations of data types that are used in Vizzly.
    ch.ethz.vizzly.util
    This package contains the implementations of certain helper classes, e.g., data validation and aggregation functions.
